	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>limit</td>
			<td><code>int</code></td>
			<td>10</td>
			<td>A value (in px) to limit the splitter boundaries on each side.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>orientation</td>
			<td><code>string</code></td>
			<td>horizontal</td>
			<td>Sets the orientation for the split layout. Allowed values are: <code>horizontal</code> (north/south) and
